    </note>Basi hawa ndio watu wa jimbo waliotoka uhamishoni, ambao Nebukadneza mfalme wa Babeli alikuwa amewachukua mateka hadi Babeli (walirudi Yerusalemu na Yuda, kila mmoja kwenye mji wake, <verse eid="EZR 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EZR 2:2"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CH 3:19">1Nya 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="1CH 6:14">6:14</ref>; <ref loc="HAG 2:4">Hag 2:4</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 3:1-10">Zek 3:1-10</ref></char></note>wakiwa wamefuatana na Zerubabeli, Yeshua, Nehemia, Seraya, Reelaya, Mordekai, Bilshani, Mispari, Bigwai, Rehumu na Baana):</para>
